definitions.definition: To instantiate jointly ; to instantiate more than one theme or concept in a given instance (such as a farmer who wears the hats of equipment operator, marketer, salesperson, and bookkeeper) .
examples: Her lucky pen coinstantiates a writing implement, a souvenir, and a hair stick to hold her hair bun!

main_definition: ( transitive ) To instantiate jointly ; to instantiate more than one theme or concept in a given instance (such as a farmer who wears the hats of equipment operator, marketer, salesperson, and bookkeeper) .
